    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>The Day Not to Be Ignored</strong>&mdash;As the twenty-fifth of December is observed to commemorate the birth of Christ, as the children have been instructed by precept and example that this was indeed a day of gladness and rejoicing, you will find it a difficult matter to pass over this period without giving it some attention. It can be made to serve a very good purpose.",
