    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Jesus Not to Be Forgotten</strong>&mdash;Brethren and sisters, while you are devising gifts for one another, I would remind you of our heavenly Friend, lest you should be unmindful of His claims. Will He not be pleased if we show that we have not forgotten Him? Jesus, the Prince of life, gave all to bring salvation within our reach.... He suffered even unto death, that He might give us eternal life.",
    "puborder": 1504,
