    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Parents should keep these things before their children and instruct them, line upon line, precept upon precept, in their obligation to God&mdash;not their obligation to each other, to honor and glorify one another by gifts and offerings.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">7<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"RH 12-9-1884\" data-link=\"821.6072\">The Review and Herald, December 9, 1884</span>.</span></a></sup>",
