    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Turn Thoughts of the Children Into a New Channel</strong>&mdash;There are many things which can be devised with taste and cost far less than the unnecessary presents that are so frequently bestowed upon our children and relatives, and thus courtesy can be shown and happiness brought into the home.",
    "puborder": 1510,
    "translations": [
